uk.co.sevendigital.android.sdk.api.request.login

Class SDILoginUserRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.sevendigital.android.sdk.api.request.abs.SDIAbsRequest<SDILoginUserRequest.Result>
      • uk.co.sevendigital.android.sdk.api.request.login.SDILoginUserRequest

  • public class SDILoginUserRequest
extends SDIAbsRequest<SDILoginUserRequest.Result>
    The SDILoginUserRequest performs the server interaction to log the user directly into the 7digital application. Specific SDILoginUserRequest.LoginConfig instances can be passed into the execution to perform mock login requests for unit tests.
